# Checklist before saving:
#   [ ] All YOUR_DOMAIN tokens replaced
#   [ ] All CLASS_NAME tokens replaced
#   [ ] All PROP_NAME tokens replaced
#   [ ] All rdfs:label values are meaningful English phrases
#   [ ] All rdfs:comment values explain the purpose of the element
#   [ ] xsd: range types match the actual data type of each property
